asset.hookText:
My EP, "Heart Back," is available NOW on iTunes! Purchase it here: https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/heart-back-ep/id624593855

** if you're experiencing timing issues, decrease the quality in the bottom right corner!
Hey y'all this is a medley I've been wanting to do, 1901 by Phoenix & Breathe by Taylor Swift. The version of 1901 is a spin off of Birdy! This is actually live and then I went back and added another acoustic track and harmony on the chorus! PLEASE keep spreading the word guys, I can't tell you all how much that does for my career. YOU are all the reason I am getting any recognition. So, THANK YOU.

www.macymaloy.com
@macymariemaloy
